---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Container from "../../components/ui/Container.astro";
import Subheading from "../../components/ui/Subheading.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Customer Re-engagement - Lunogram"
  description="Win back dormant and churned customers with automated re-engagement campaigns. Reach the right users with the right message at the right time."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="pt-32 pb-16 sm:pt-40 sm:pb-24">
    <Container>
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <a href="/use-cases" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm text-white/50 hover:text-white/70 transition-colors mb-6">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path>
          </svg>
          All use cases
        </a>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-rose-500/15 ring-1 ring-rose-500/20 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-rose-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M21 8.25c0-2.485-2.099-4.5-4.688-4.5-1.935 0-3.597 1.126-4.312 2.733-.715-1.607-2.377-2.733-4.313-2.733C5.1 3.75 3 5.765 3 8.25c0 7.22 9 12 9 12s9-4.78 9-12z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <Subheading class="text-rose-400 mb-4">Re-engagement</Subheading>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-medium tracking-tight text-white text-balance">
          Win back the customers<br class="hidden sm:block" />
          you've already earned
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Dormant users aren't lost causes. Lunogram helps you bring them back with targeted, well-timed campaigns that feel personal — not desperate.
        </p>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </section>

  <!-- The Problem -->
  <section class="py-24 border-t border-white/5">
    <Container>
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-medium tracking-tight text-white mb-6">
          Why users go dormant
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Not every churned user left because they hated your product. Life got busy, they forgot, or they never found the feature that would have made them stay. The opportunity to bring them back is real — but only if you act with the right timing and the right message.
        </p>

        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
          <div class="bg-white/[0.03] rounded-xl p-5 ring-1 ring-white/10">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-red-500/15 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center ring-1 ring-red-500/20 mb-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-1">Bad timing</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-white/50">They signed up at the wrong moment and never got a second chance to engage.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white/[0.03] rounded-xl p-5 ring-1 ring-white/10">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-red-500/15 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center ring-1 ring-red-500/20 mb-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M3.98 8.223A10.477 10.477 0 001.934 12C3.226 16.338 7.244 19.5 12 19.5c.993 0 1.953-.138 2.863-.395M6.228 6.228A10.45 10.45 0 0112 4.5c4.756 0 8.773 3.162 10.065 7.498a10.523 10.523 0 01-4.293 5.774M6.228 6.228L3 3m3.228 3.228l3.65 3.65m7.894 7.894L21 21m-3.228-3.228l-3.65-3.65m0 0a3 3 0 10-4.243-4.243m4.242 4.242L9.88 9.88"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-1">Undiscovered value</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-white/50">They never found the feature that would have made them stay. Your product's value was invisible.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white/[0.03] rounded-xl p-5 ring-1 ring-white/10">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-red-500/15 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center ring-1 ring-red-500/20 mb-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M18.364 18.364A9 9 0 005.636 5.636m12.728 12.728A9 9 0 015.636 5.636m12.728 12.728L5.636 5.636"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-1">Generic blast emails</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-white/50">Mass "we miss you" emails that feel impersonal and get ignored or marked as spam.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </section>

  <!-- How Lunogram Helps -->
  <section class="py-24 border-t border-white/5">
    <Container>
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <p class="font-mono text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest text-rose-400 uppercase mb-4">
          How Lunogram helps
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-medium tracking-tight text-white mb-12">
          Smart win-back campaigns, not spray-and-pray
        </h2>

        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="flex gap-5">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-rose-500/15 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center ring-1 ring-rose-500/20 shrink-0">
              <span class="text-rose-400 font-semibold text-sm">1</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Segment by inactivity pattern</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
                Create segments for users who haven't logged in for 14, 30, or 60+ days. Combine inactivity with past behavior — a power user who went silent is a very different win-back target than someone who never activated.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-5">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-rose-500/15 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center ring-1 ring-rose-500/20 shrink-0">
              <span class="text-rose-400 font-semibold text-sm">2</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Personalize the message</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
                Use what you know about each user to craft relevant outreach. Reference the features they used, the goals they set, or what's new since they left. Generic "come back" emails don't work — context does.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-5">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-rose-500/15 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center ring-1 ring-rose-500/20 shrink-0">
              <span class="text-rose-400 font-semibold text-sm">3</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Use multiple channels</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
                Dormant users aren't checking their inbox. Reach them where they'll actually see it — email first, then push notification, then in-app message when they return. Lunogram orchestrates the sequence automatically.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-5">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-rose-500/15 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center ring-1 ring-rose-500/20 shrink-0">
              <span class="text-rose-400 font-semibold text-sm">4</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Know when to stop</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
                Set frequency caps and sunset policies so you don't annoy users who've clearly moved on. Lunogram automatically exits users from re-engagement flows once they've re-activated — or once the window has closed.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </section>

  <!-- Example Journey -->
  <section class="py-24 border-t border-white/5">
    <Container>
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-medium tracking-tight text-white mb-10">
          Example: Win-back campaign flow
        </h2>
        <div class="bg-white/[0.02] rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-10 ring-1 ring-white/[0.06]">
          <!-- Trigger -->
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-11 h-11 bg-rose-500/15 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center ring-1 ring-rose-500/25 shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-rose-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
              <span class="text-[13px] font-medium text-white">User inactive for 30 days</span>
            </div>
            <span class="text-[10px] tracking-wider text-rose-400/70 font-mono uppercase bg-rose-500/10 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full ring-1 ring-rose-500/20">trigger</span>
          </div>

          <!-- Connector -->
          <div class="ml-[21px] w-px h-6 bg-gradient-to-b from-white/10 to-white/5"></div>

          <!-- Step: Send email -->
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-11 h-11 bg-white/[0.06] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center ring-1 ring-white/10 shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white/40" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
              <span class="text-[13px] text-white/80">Send personalized "what's new" email</span>
            </div>
            <span class="text-[10px] tracking-wider text-white/30 font-mono uppercase">send</span>
          </div>

          <!-- Connector -->
          <div class="ml-[21px] w-px h-6 bg-gradient-to-b from-white/10 to-white/5"></div>

          <!-- Step: Wait -->
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-11 h-11 bg-white/[0.06] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center ring-1 ring-white/10 shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white/40" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
              <span class="text-[13px] text-white/80">Wait 5 days</span>
            </div>
            <span class="text-[10px] tracking-wider text-white/30 font-mono uppercase">delay</span>
          </div>

          <!-- Connector -->
          <div class="ml-[21px] w-px h-6 bg-gradient-to-b from-white/10 to-white/5"></div>

          <!-- Step: Condition 1 -->
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-11 h-11 bg-white/[0.06] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center ring-1 ring-white/10 rotate-45 shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white/40 -rotate-45" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M8.228 9c.549-1.165 2.03-2 3.772-2 2.21 0 4 1.343 4 3 0 1.4-1.278 2.575-3.006 2.907-.542.104-.994.54-.994 1.093m0 3h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
              <span class="text-[13px] text-white/80">Did user return?</span>
            </div>
            <span class="text-[10px] tracking-wider text-white/30 font-mono uppercase">condition</span>
          </div>

          <!-- Branch outcomes 1 -->
          <div class="ml-[21px] w-px h-4 bg-white/5"></div>
          <div class="ml-6 sm:ml-10 grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2">
            <div class="bg-white/[0.04] rounded-xl p-4 ring-1 ring-white/[0.08]">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
                <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-green-500/15 flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-green-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-xs font-medium text-white/70">Yes</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-xs text-white/50 leading-relaxed">Show in-app welcome back message + changelog</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white/[0.04] rounded-xl p-4 ring-1 ring-white/[0.08]">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
                <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-red-500/15 flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-red-400/70" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-xs font-medium text-white/70">No</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-xs text-white/50 leading-relaxed">Send push notification with key update</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Connector to second cycle -->
          <div class="ml-[21px] w-px h-6 bg-gradient-to-b from-white/5 to-white/10"></div>

          <!-- Step: Wait 2 -->
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-11 h-11 bg-white/[0.06] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center ring-1 ring-white/10 shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white/40" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
              <span class="text-[13px] text-white/80">Wait 7 days</span>
            </div>
            <span class="text-[10px] tracking-wider text-white/30 font-mono uppercase">delay</span>
          </div>

          <!-- Connector -->
          <div class="ml-[21px] w-px h-6 bg-gradient-to-b from-white/10 to-white/5"></div>

          <!-- Step: Condition 2 -->
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-11 h-11 bg-white/[0.06] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center ring-1 ring-white/10 rotate-45 shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white/40 -rotate-45" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M8.228 9c.549-1.165 2.03-2 3.772-2 2.21 0 4 1.343 4 3 0 1.4-1.278 2.575-3.006 2.907-.542.104-.994.54-.994 1.093m0 3h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
              <span class="text-[13px] text-white/80">Still inactive?</span>
            </div>
            <span class="text-[10px] tracking-wider text-white/30 font-mono uppercase">condition</span>
          </div>

          <!-- Branch outcomes 2 -->
          <div class="ml-[21px] w-px h-4 bg-white/5"></div>
          <div class="ml-6 sm:ml-10 grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2">
            <div class="bg-white/[0.04] rounded-xl p-4 ring-1 ring-white/[0.08]">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
                <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-green-500/15 flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-green-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-xs font-medium text-white/70">Returned</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-xs text-white/50 leading-relaxed">Exit flow, move user to retention segment</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white/[0.04] rounded-xl p-4 ring-1 ring-white/[0.08]">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
                <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-white/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white/40" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M18.364 18.364A9 9 0 005.636 5.636m12.728 12.728A9 9 0 015.636 5.636m12.728 12.728L5.636 5.636"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-xs font-medium text-white/70">Still gone</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-xs text-white/50 leading-relaxed">Sunset: stop messaging, mark as churned</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-24 border-t border-white/5">
    <Container>
      <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-medium tracking-tight text-white mb-6">
          Bring dormant users back to life
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-8">
          Build win-back campaigns that feel personal, not pushy. Get started in minutes with Lunogram Cloud.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 sm:flex-row">
          <a
            href="https://accounts.lunogram.com"
            class="inline-flex h-11 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-violet-600 to-purple-600 px-6 text-sm font-medium text-white shadow-lg shadow-violet-500/25 hover:from-violet-500 hover:to-purple-500 transition-all duration-200"
          >
            Get Started
            <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a
            href="/use-cases"
            class="inline-flex h-11 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-white/10 px-6 text-sm font-medium text-white ring-1 ring-white/15 transition-colors hover:bg-white/15"
          >
            View all use cases
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </section>
</Layout>
